OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,FWith the election set for next week,
OL,8,FI've spoken to voters on what they
OL,9,Fwant to see from incoming Deputies to
OL,10,Ftackle Guernsey's housing shortage.
OL,12,FNicky Shaw is a single mother who
OL,13,Fworks hard to provide for her family
OL,14,Fas a teacher.
OL,16,FHowever, she says keeping up with her
OL,17,Frent is a struggle.
OL,19,FShe explains: "It's month to month,
OL,20,Fand it's almost pound to pound - penny
OL,21,Fto penny.
