OL,7,F"Even though I've budgeted and I look
OL,8,Fat my budget and I'm like 'I'm doing
OL,9,Falright' it's the last handful of days
OL,10,Fwhere I cannot wait to go food
OL,11,Fshopping again.
OL,13,F"I hope the Deputies that get in
OL,14,Freally consider housing as important
OL,15,Fas other issues. It just can't just be
OL,16,Ftalked about and dropped off again."
