OL,7,FWhile projects have been delayed or
OL,8,Fthrown out developments outside of St
OL,9,FPeter Port, there are suggestions that
OL,10,Fbuilding in the town itself could
OL,11,Fprovide much-needed housing stock.
OL,13,FArchitect Olly Brock argues that for
OL,14,Fsome people, living in flat blocks in
OL,15,Ftown is a more viable option for their
OL,16,Flifestyles.
