OL,7,FHe explains: "St Peter Port is the
OL,8,Fmain centre. From a planning
OL,9,Fperspective, all of the policies are
OL,10,Fthere to deliver large-scale projects
OL,11,Fthat will deliver hundreds of houses.
OL,13,F"We've got swathes of young people who
OL,14,Ffeel like there isn't a future for
OL,15,Fthem on the property ladder.
OL,17,F"They probably don't want to spend
OL,18,Ftheir weekend tending to a garden.
OL,19,FThey're probably quite flexible about
OL,20,Fbeing somewhere they can live for five
OL,21,For ten years.
