OL,7,F"So there are a lot of options that
OL,8,Fhigh-rise and high-density living give
OL,9,Fus."
OL,11,FDespite high-rise buildings providing
OL,12,Fhousing space, some say it's not as
OL,13,Fsimple to start these types of
OL,14,Fbuilding projects on the island.
OL,16,FBuilding homes needs to be profitable,
OL,17,Fand some suggest that it is not
OL,18,Fcurrently the case.
