OL,4,Csolutions on the island's housing
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,FEstate agent Stuart Leslie says he's
OL,8,Fselling less at the moment, as even
OL,9,Fbuilding low-cost developments is not
OL,10,Ffinancially viable.
OL,12,FHe explains: "The cost of building
OL,13,Fhere is so high compared to the rest
OL,14,Fof the UK or even Jersey, to a degree.
OL,16,F"We need to find a way to bring those
OL,17,Fcosts down because ultimately, unless
OL,18,Fyou're a government or a housing
OL,19,Fassociation, you're not going to be
OL,20,Fproperties at a loss.
