OL,7,F"You really need a private developer
OL,8,Fto satisfy the housing need."
OL,10,FSo what are candidates saying? Some
OL,11,Fare frustrated at the lack of building
OL,12,Fand want to look at relaxing some
OL,13,Fplanning laws.
OL,15,FHowever, this raises concerns that
OL,16,Fdevelopers will seek profit as a
OL,17,Fpriority at the expense of things such
OL,18,Fas the environment.
