OL,7,FIn the last States' term, Deputies did
OL,8,Fvote to relax rules by suspending GP11
OL,9,F- that meant 30% of large building
OL,10,Fdevelopments must be set aside for
OL,11,Faffordable housing - but this was
OL,12,Fthrown out.
OL,14,FThe belief is that the move could get
OL,15,Fmore developments off the ground
OL,16,Ffaster, but we are yet to see the
OL,17,Ftangible benefits of that decision.
